<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   y = ann_hardlim_activ(x)
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>x :</term>
      <listitem><para> Input vector</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>y :</term>
      <listitem><para> Output vector</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
This is the hardlimit activation function, in which y = 0 for x &lt; 0 and y = 1 for x &gt;= 0
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

